I have a Huawei P10 lite running on Android 7.0
When I wanted to listen to an album, I couldn't find it in the music app. Apparently, something got messed up because multiple albums are stuffed into a single "album" with the band's name as title. Instead of "Album Title" containing songs 1 to 10, I get "Band name" containing songs from four different albums. On my old phone, everything worked perfectly fine and the music files' info is correct, too. This happened to a total of ten albums from five different artists.
Why can't it just work? ;_;
